headline: CUISINE SOLUTIONS® UNVEILS NEW SEAR & SERVE™ LINE, BRINGING PREMIUM SOUS VIDE PROTEINS DIRECTLY TO HOME COOKS
summary: Cuisine Solutions® (NYSE: CUSI), the global leader in sous vide, today announced the launch of Sear & Serve™, a new line of perfectly cooked, chef-quality, premium sous vide beef and pork cuts designed to bring consistently exceptional results to home kitchens. The launch coincides with the debut of a new direct-to-consumer website, SearandServeCuisine.com, making the line immediately accessible to consumers nationwide.
